2. The 14th day of February 2025 is appointed as the day on which the 
Health (Miscellaneous Provisions) (No. 2) Act 2024 (No. 29 of 2024), in so far 
as it is not already in operation, shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

11 February, 2025. 

JENNIFER CARROLL MACNEILL, 

Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 14th February, 2025.
